com.i2group.apollo.model.schema

Enum SystemType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SystemType>
      • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.SystemType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SystemType>

    public enum SystemType
extends Enum<SystemType>
    Indicates the type of an item that has one of the system types in the schema.

    A system type is an item type that has a special meaning in the repository, and must be present (along with its property types) in all schemas.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ALERT_FEED
      The item is an "Alert Feed" entity.
      ALERT_SUBSCRIPTION

      CHART
      The item is an "Analyst's Notebook Chart" entity.
      SET
      The item is an entity that owns a "Set".
      STORED_QUERY
      The item is a stored, user-defined query (for example, a network search).
      USER
      The item is a "User" entity.
